    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "c9c8d25b-8f63-40f3-809a-473108a2de6d",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Hitman 3. Episode 9. Thirty years later",
        "Location": "LOCATION_EDGY_FOX",
        "PublicId": "129911061920",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 252428ca-3f8e-4477-b2b9-58f18cff3e44).Image",
        "Description": "30 years ago Four underage boys drove a car straight into another car drunk. In the car were two children and their parents. The parents died but the children survived. The charges were somehow dismissed. Well now they have connected with us, and want us to murder Witold Schuchert and Helmut Scholz. Take with you the sniper rifle 47, and climb the &quot;Radio tower&quot;. In addition to them, you need to shoot the guard with a sniper in another building, before it shoots you. Good luck. Have fun!",
